Miriam Byrd Nethery https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miriam_Byrd_Nethery 0 Miriam Byrd Nethery (May 17, 1929 – January 6, 2003) was an American film and television actress. Her film roles included Bound for Glory (1976) and Leatherface: The Texas Chainsaw Massacre III and Across Five Aprils (both 1990).
